(30, 'Nitro Mountain X Grif 157', '<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\">Based off of our team rider, turning guru, and mountain enthusiast, Griffin Siebert&acute;s passion for the Nitro Mountain snowboard, the Mountain x Griffin provides a fresh look at an old school shape, Cam-Out Camber, Mid-Wide width, and Tapered Directional board style. Built to help riders of all ages to charge hard in the pow and ripping groomers with ease - with a little bit of Peace, Love, and Powder vibes!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\">&ldquo;Snowboarding is seeming to get more and more serious as the years go by, and this seasons Grif x MTN graphic is a reminder for myself as to why we snowboard, or at least why I snowboard. I snowboard for the amazing feeling it gives you as you are flying down a mountain as if you are floating on flowers. This year&acute;s graphic is to encourage everyone to embrace their inner flower child and utilize this board to boogie down the hill, whether that be pow, slush, or groomers, even moguls for all I care. Pass on the stoke, it&rsquo;s contagious.</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\">Peace, Love, and Powder. &ldquo;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\">- Love Griffin Siebert</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>Жёсткость:</strong> жесткая</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>Уровень:&nbsp;</strong>продвинутый / эксперт</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>Геометрия:</strong>&nbsp;directional</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>Назначение:</strong>&nbsp;фрирайд / универсальная</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>Прогиб:</strong>&nbsp;cam-out camber</span></div>', 0, 0, 0, 0, '270900', NULL, '2.50', 'male', '{\"title\": \"Nitro Mountain X Grif 157\", \"description\": \"Based off of our team rider, turning guru, and mountain enthusiast, Griffin Siebert´s passion for the Nitro Mountain snowboard, the Mountain x Griffin provides a fresh look at an old school shape, Cam-Out Camber, Mid-Wide width, and Tapered Directional board style. Built to help riders of all ages to charge hard in the pow and ripping groomers with ease - with a little bit of Peace, Love, and Powder vibes!  “Snowboarding is seeming to get more and more serious as the years go by, and this seasons Grif x MTN graphic is a reminder for myself as to why we snowboard, or at least why I snowboard. I snowboard for the amazing feeling it gives you as you are flying down a mountain as if you are floating on flowers. This year´s graphic is to encourage everyone to embrace their inner flower child and utilize this board to boogie down the hill, whether that be pow, slush, or groomers, even moguls for all I care. Pass on the stoke, it’s contagious. Peace, Love, and Powder. “ - Love Griffin Siebert  Жёсткость: жесткая Уровень: продвинутый / эксперт Геометрия: directional Назначение: фрирайд / универсальная Прогиб: cam-out camber\"}', 9, 3, '2021-01-31 14:15:19', '2021-01-31 15:01:12', NULL),
