(101, 'Nitro Droid QLS Charcoal-Black-Orange', '<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\">Ботинки DROID это технологичная модель для детей и подростков. Ботинки имеют съемный внутренний сапожок и систему быстрой шнуровки. Подошва из пены EVA обладает хорошей амортизацией.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>Жесткость:</strong> 3/10</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>Пол:</strong> детские</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>Шнуровка:</strong> QLS</span></p>', 0, 0, 0, 0, '75900', NULL, '1.50', 'child', '{\"title\": \"Nitro Droid QLS Charcoal-Black-Orange\", \"description\": \"Nitro Droid QLS Charcoal-Black-Orange\"}', 9, 4, '2021-02-16 13:21:58', '2021-02-16 13:21:58', NULL),
(102, 'Nitro Droid Boa Navy Bl-Grey-Yell', '<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\">The new Nitro Droid BOA Youth snowboarding boot is the next step in progression for kids looking for a little more response and technology, to help them progress their snowboarding every day.</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\">The new Nitro Droid Boa snowboard boot was developed specifically for those young rippers who put the rest of us to shame, the kids who demand more than a kid&rsquo;s boot! Designed with features like the BOA Lacing System and new Removable Light Liner to allow for a custom foothold, while the Powerstrap allows for the perfect adjustable response. Built with all the support and fit technologies of our pro-level boots, this ripper-friendly quick lacing (BOA) boot will get you first out of the lodge and on the chair faster all season long!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'trebuchet ms\', geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>Жесткость:</strong>&nbsp;3/10<br /><strong>Пол:</strong>&nbsp;детские<br /><strong>Шнуровка:</strong>&nbsp;BOA</span></p>', 0, 0, 0, 0, '80900', NULL, '1.50', 'child', '{\"title\": \"Nitro Droid Boa Navy Bl-Grey-Yell\", \"description\": \"Nitro Droid Boa Navy Bl-Grey-Yell\"}', 9, 4, '2021-02-16 17:28:41', '2021-02-16 17:28:41', NULL),
